===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[slander]]; to [[defame]]; to [[vilify]]; to [[speak]] [[maliciously]] of [[others]]
#* {{zh-x|「我 的 心肝，你 說的是，咱們 讒 他 兩 個。」|"My dear, you are right indeed, let's '''slander''' them both."|ref=Hongloumeng}}
# [[slander]]; [[defamation]]; [[libel]]
#* {{zh-x|只 說 這 ^@王摩 被 四 個 弟兄 獻 讒 趕逐，一時 忿氣，奔 下山 來。||WVC|ref={{lang|zh|青蓮室主人}}, {{lw|zh|pref=《|s:後水滸傳/第20回|後水滸傳|suf=》}} (''The Later Story of Water Margin''), 17<sup>th</sup> century {{CE}}}}
#* {{zh-x|讒 人 高 張，賢士 無名。|The people who commit '''slander''' loudly prevail, the virtuous hide in obscurity.|ref=Chuci}}
#* {{zh-x|君子 信 讒，如 或 醻 之。君子 不 惠、不 舒 究 之。|Our sovereign believes '''slanders''',<br>as readily as he joins in the pledge cup.<br>Our sovereign is unkind,<br>And does not leisurely examine into things.|ref=Shijing}}
# {{lb|zh|obs-std}} [[slanderer]]
#* {{zh-x|去 讒 遠 色，賤 貨 而 貴 德，所 以 勸 賢 也。|Discarding '''slanderers''', and keeping himself from the seductions of beauty; making light of riches, and giving honour to virtue — this is the way for him to encourage men of worth and talents.|ref=Liji-L}}
#* {{zh-x|是 以 中外 不通，讒 慝 不 生，婦 言 不及 官 中 之 事。|ref=Guanzi}}

